1.0.0.name: wordpress/testimonials-by-woothemes
1.0.0.description:
"Testimonials by WooThemes" is a clean and easy-to-use testimonials management system for WordPress. Load in what your customers are saying about your business, and display the testimonials via a shortcode, widget or template tag on your website.

Looking for a helping hand? View plugin documentation.

Looking to contribute code to this plugin? Fork the repository over at GitHub. (submit pull requests to the latest "release-" branch)
